name: Yoon Mi-rae
description: '''Natasha Shanta Reid''' (born May 31, 1981), better known by her Korean name '''Yoon Mi-rae''' ({{Korean|hangul=윤미래}}), often stylized as ''Yoonmirae'', is an American-born based South Korean rapper, singer, songwriter, and producer, who is also a member of [[Korean hip hop]] trio [[MFBTY]].
